3. Sorting System — Introduction of Lightweight Generic Helpers

---

Affected logic:

* Chart section generation
* Table column ordering
* Label selection ordering

Changes made:

* Introduced `sortByPriority()` helper:

  * Sorts values based on a priority list
  * Falls back to alphabetical ordering for non-priority items
* Introduced `sortPoints()` helper:

  * Sorts chart data points by magnitude (descending)
  * Secondary sort by label for stability
* Applied sorting consistently across:

  * Chart points
  * Section keys
  * Table columns

Behavior breakdown:

| Data Type     | Sorting Behavior                              |
| ------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| Chart values  | Sorted by absolute value (largest first)      |
| Chart labels  | Alphabetical fallback                         |
| Table columns | Ordered by priority list, then alphabetically |
| Label keys    | Selected using priority-driven ordering       |

