---

Affected logic:

* `getSectionsFromArray`
* `getSectionsFromObject`
* `getChartSections`
* `buildChartsHtml`

Changes made:

* Applied `sortPoints()` to all chart datasets for consistent ordering
* Introduced `CHART_POINT_LIMIT` constant (replacing inline slice value)
* Sorted chart sections alphabetically by title
* Preserved existing deduplication logic for sections
* Ensured chart rendering remains visually consistent across different data shapes

Behavior breakdown:

