| ------------------ | ---------------------------------------- |
| Large datasets     | Only top N values shown (via constant)   |
| Mixed datasets     | Consistent sorting across all sections   |
| Duplicate sections | Still filtered out as before             |
| Chart titles       | Sorted alphabetically for predictability |

